com.googlecode.biscotti.collect

  • Packages that use com.googlecode.biscotti.collect 
    Package Description
    com.googlecode.biscotti.collect
    This package contains interfaces, implementations, and other utilities for working with Collections and Maps.
  • Classes in com.googlecode.biscotti.collect used by com.googlecode.biscotti.collect

    BoundedMap
    A capacity restricted Map.
    BoundedQueue
    A capacity restricted Queue.
    FIFOBoundedMap
    A LinkedHashMap implementation of BoundedMap which removes stale mappings in first-in-first-out order.
    ForwardingPeekingIterator
    A PeekingIterator which forwards all its method calls to another PeekingIterator.
    LinkedBoundedQueue
    A linked list implementation of BoundedQueue.
    LRUBoundedMap
    A LinkedHashMap implementation of BoundedMap which removes stale mappings in least-recently-accessed order.
    RankList

    TreeBoundedDeque

    TreeDeque
